.TH btctax-income 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
income \- Full\-return (v1) input surface: import, show, or clear the per\-year full\-return inputs (W\-2s, 1099s, deductions, household). Offline; stored in the encrypted vault
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBincome\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Full\-return (v1) input surface: import, show, or clear the per\-year full\-return inputs (W\-2s, 1099s, deductions, household). Offline; stored in the encrypted vault
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
income\-import(1)
Import full\-return inputs from an offline TOML file into the vault for a tax year
.TP
income\-show(1)
Show the stored full\-return inputs for a tax year (JSON, PII redacted), or nothing if none set
.TP
income\-clear(1)
Remove the stored full\-return inputs for a tax year (fall back to a raw `tax\-profile`)
